==Starting out==
===Speaking to Jack Frost===
* '''Player:''' Hello!
* '''Jack Frost:''' Oh, hey there.
* {{tselect|Select an Option}}
* {{topt|What brings you here?}}
** '''Player:''' What brings you here?
** '''Jack Frost:''' Officially? I was bored so my dad tasked me to bring a tiny bit of cheer to Gielinor.
** '''Player:''' A 'tiny' bit of cheer?
** '''Jack Frost:''' I understood that to mean he doesn't want me freezing the whole continent.
** '''Player:''' That... Sounds sensible.
** '''Jack Frost:''' I don't like Christmas. My dad's always too busy to spend time with me. It's the busiest time of the year for him.
** '''Player:''' Have you considered helping him out?
** '''Jack Frost:''' Honestly, it didn't work out so well last time. I don't think I'm cut out for that kind of work. I'm more of an artist.
** '''Jack Frost:''' But the second reason I don't like Christmas is that there's this one lady that's seemingly obsessed with me.
** '''Jack Frost:''' Every year she sings to all who will listen that all she wants for Christmas is me. Everywhere I go, I hear her. It's awful. I've tried to explain to her that I'm not into her, to no avail.
** '''Jack Frost:''' Last year, in desperation, I even froze her with a special, really potent ice spell of mine. Nothing dangerous of course.
** '''Jack Frost:''' I thought I was finally free... But recently she somehow thawed out and started singing again. I can't go on like this.
** '''Player:''' Wait wait wait. Are you absolutely sure she's after you specifically and she's not just singing that song because it's festive? Does she follow you at other times of the year?
** '''Jack Frost:''' She doesn't, no. She usually keeps going until the new year and then when it's obvious my dad didn't give in, she stops.
** '''Jack Frost:''' I suppose she does sing she doesn't want a lot, then she goes on to ask for me, yet Dad always says I'm a lot. Maybe you're right and she's not after me at all!
** '''Player:''' Phew! That's one mystery solved!
** {{tact|initial}}
* {{topt|What happened to this field?}}
** '''Player:''' What happened to this field?
** '''Jack Frost:''' I froze it.
** '''Player:''' Oh. Fair enough. May I ask why?
** '''Jack Frost:''' I was trying to craft a playground for everyone, with ramps and everything. That should be fun and entertaining, right?
** '''Player:''' For everyone, you say?
** '''Jack Frost:''' Yes! I even saw a cow on it earlier.
** '''Player:''' A cow! No way! How did it do?
** '''Jack Frost:''' It's hard to explain in words... I suppose I could mime it?
** {{qact|Jack Frost mimics slipping on the ice and falling over multiple times.}}
** '''Jack Frost:''' I think that sums it up...
** '''Player:''' Oh wow.
** '''Jack Frost:''' I don't think that cow will try coming back here again in a hurry.
** '''Jack Frost:''' But never mind the cow. Do you fancy giving this a go and seeing what happens?
** {{tselect|Start the Christmas event?}}
** {{topt|Yes}}
*** '''Player:''' Sure, why not! How does it work?
*** '''Jack Frost:''' You just need to step in. Ice is slippery so you should keep going straight until you find an obstacle or some ground you can stop on.
*** '''Jack Frost:''' I wonder if I can get you to draw something dot-to- dot. There, I'll give you beacons to aim for! Start with this one.
*** {{tact|Jack Frost places a beacon in the cow field}}
*** {{tact|end}}
** {{topt|No}}
*** '''Player:''' Actually, not right now.
*** '''Jack Frost:''' Feel free to change your mind any time!
*** {{tact|end}}
* {{topt|That's all for the moment.}}
** '''Player:''' That's all for the moment.
** {{tact|end}}

===Speaking to Jack Frost again===
* '''Jack Frost:''' Off you go! You just need to step in. Ice is slippery so you should keep going straight until you find an obstacle or some ground you can stop on.
* '''Jack Frost:''' Aim for the beacons!
