==During the Event==
===Completing the heart===
* '''Jack Frost:''' Great! Now come back to talk to me!
* {{tact|end}}

===Speaking to Jack Frost after completing the heart===
* {{tcond|If the player completed the heart neatly:}}
** '''Jack Frost:''' Wow, amazing! You did that really neatly. Well done!
** '''Player:''' Thank you! Now what shall we do?
** '''Jack Frost:''' How about trying the ramps? I will guide you.
** {{tact|Jack Frost places another beacon in the cow field.}}
** {{tact|initial}}
* {{tcond|If the player completed a messy heart:}}
** '''Jack Frost:''' Let's be real. That wasn't the neatest dot-to-dot.
** {{tselect|Select an Option}}
** {{topt|It's my first time.}}
*** '''Jack Frost:''' That's fair. You are only at the start of your ice- skating journey, and you still did better than the cow.
*** '''Player:''' What shall we do now?
*** '''Jack Frost:''' How about trying the ramps? I will guide you.
*** {{tact|above}}
** {{topt|It's about as hard as staying within the lines when freezing a field.}}
*** '''Player:''' It's about as hard as staying within the lines when freezing a field.
*** '''Jack Frost:''' Wow, you have no chill. That's ok, I have chill for the both of us.
*** '''Player:''' What shall we do now?
*** '''Jack Frost:''' How about trying the ramps? I will guide you.
*** {{tact|above}}

===Speaking to Jack Frost again===
* '''Jack Frost:''' Keep at it! Follow the beacons on the ramps.
* {{tact|initial}}

===After jumping the first ramp===
* {{tcond|Jumping from the east:}}
** '''Jack Frost:''' That's not quite right... I need you to be approaching the beacon from the west.
** {{tact|end}}
* {{tcond|Jumping from the west:}}
** '''Jack Frost:''' Nice! Keep following the beacons! I'm going to try something.
** {{tact|Jack Frost creates a snow shark under the ramp.}}
** {{tact|end}}

===Jumping the ramp again===
* {{tcond|Jumping from the west:}}
** '''Jack Frost:''' That's not quite right... I need you to be approaching the beacon from the east.
** {{tact|end}}
* {{tcond|Jumping from the east:}}
** '''Jack Frost:''' Haha! You just jumped the shark!
** '''Jack Frost:''' That was great! Now come back to talk to me!
** {{tact|The snow shark disappears.}}
** {{tact|end}}

===Speaking to Jack Frost after completing the ramp jump===
* '''Jack Frost:''' Wow, that was amazing! I'm starting to think icing this field was a really good idea!
* '''Player:''' That's good news! What next?
* '''Jack Frost:''' I don't know, how about a bunch of mini-challenges to keep you on your toes?
* {{qact|Anti-Santa appears from his portal behind Jack Frost.}}
* '''Anti-Santa:''' Ha Ha Ha  It is you again, Jack Frost!
* '''Jack Frost:''' A-A-Anti Santa!? What are you doing here? Did my dad send you again? I did as he asked!
* '''Anti-Santa:''' No. I heard mirth coming from this place and I came to wipe it off. Life is pain and fun has no place here.
* '''Player:''' What? No no no, fun has...
* '''Jack Frost:''' No place here indeed!
* '''Player:''' Wait, what?
* '''Jack Frost:''' This is my latest experimental arena. I... designed it to make people feel and accept the pain of life.
* '''Jack Frost:''' (whisper) Trust me on this one, I have an idea to make him go away. Just follow my lead.
* '''Jack Frost:''' This adventurer was unwittingly helping me test it.
* '''Player:''' I can't believe you were using me like this! Why you...
* '''Anti-Santa:''' Ha Ha Ha  Do you really think your little tricks are going to work on me?
* '''Jack Frost:''' It's not a trick. If you don't believe me, I will show you. Let's start by getting you in the arena. Right this way! Unless you're scared?
* '''Anti-Santa:''' Ha Ha Ha  I do not fear pain. But if you are found to have been lying, I will get back at you!
* {{qact|A cutscene starts. [[Winter Funfair]] begins to play, while Anti-Santa enters the "arena".}}
* '''Anti-Santa:''' Let us see.
* '''Anti-Santa:''' How is this pain? How is this the reality of life?
* '''Jack Frost:''' Well, you see, this is only the beginning. Now you are in the arena, may the trials begin!
* {{qact|Jack Frost begins pelting Anti-Santa with snowballs}}
* '''Jack Frost:''' [player name], if you please. Grab some snow from the piles and help me with the pelting.
* '''Player:''' On it!
* {{qact|Cutscene ends.}}
* {{tact|end}}

==Defeating Anti-Santa==
===Speaking to Jack Frost before throwing any snowballs===
* '''Jack Frost:''' Pelt him with snowballs!
* {{tact|initial}}

===1st snowball===
''(While pelting Anti-Santa, he will randomly begin his sentence with either "Yes!", "Ow!", or "Ha Ha Ha!")''
* '''Anti-Santa:''' [Yes!/Ow!/Ha Ha Ha!] This is puny.
* {{tact|end}}

===Speaking to Jack Frost after throwing a snowball===
* '''Jack Frost:''' Pelt him with more snowballs!
* {{tact|initial}}

===2nd snowball===
* '''Anti-Santa:''' [Yes!/Ow!/Ha Ha Ha!] Is that all you've got?
* {{tact|end}}

===3rd snowball===
* '''Anti-Santa:''' [Yes!/Ow!/Ha Ha Ha!] The cold never bothered me anyway.
* {{tact|end}}

===4th snowball===
* '''Anti-Santa:''' [Yes!/Ow!/Ha Ha Ha!] I'm still not impressed.
* {{tact|end}}

===5th snowball===
* '''Anti-Santa:''' [Yes!/Ow!/Ha Ha Ha!] There is water trickling down my spine.
* {{tact|end}}

===6th snowball===
* '''Anti-Santa:''' [Yes!/Ow!/Ha Ha Ha!] This is becoming irritating.
* {{tact|end}}

===7th snowball===
* '''Anti-Santa:''' [Yes!/Ow!/Ha Ha Ha!] I still wouldn't call it pain.
* {{tact|end}}

===Speaking to Jack Frost after throwing the 7th snowball===
* '''Jack Frost:''' Pelt him with even MORE snowballs!
* {{tact|initial}}

===8th snowball===
* '''Anti-Santa:''' [Yes!/Ow!/Ha Ha Ha!] How long are you going to keep this up for?
* {{tact|end}}

===9th snowball===
* '''Anti-Santa:''' [Yes!/Ow!/Ha Ha Ha!] It's going in my boots.
* {{tact|end}}

===10th snowball===
* '''Anti-Santa:''' [Yes!/Ow!/Ha Ha Ha!] I get the idea, you can stop now. Snowballs are a good start, however they are not crushing enough.
* '''Anti-Santa:''' Do I need to show you the kind of dread this little arena has to inspire for me to consider leaving you to it?
* '''Jack Frost:''' Not crushing enough, eh? That's because you haven't seen the worst of it yet. For a start, it only takes one bad step to fall unceremoniously on one's bottom.
* '''Jack Frost:''' This happened to a cow earlier, and although I could mime it again, I'd really rather not.
* '''Anti-Santa:''' A cow? Did your father not teach you to call humans names?
* '''Player:''' You mean to say... So that's why you were able to mime it!
* '''Jack Frost:''' No, no! I mean an actual animal!
* '''Anti-Santa:''' You are not helping your case.
* '''Jack Frost:''' Four legs, eats grass! I think? I had to de-ice a path to get it back out. Come on, can we please stay on topic?
* '''Jack Frost:''' Falling on the ice is not all of it. For my next trick, I will make [player name] here slightly denser.
* {{qact|Jack Frost casts a spell and snowflakes fall on the player.}}
* '''Player:''' Excuse me?
* '''Anti-Santa:''' Your disrespect for humans shows no bounds.
* '''Jack Frost:''' Urgh! No, I promise this is a big misunderstanding! Will you just let me finish!
* '''Jack Frost:''' (whisper)I'm just allowing you to ram into him by making you heavier. Then I want you to slide at him with all you've got.
* '''Player:''' This is not what I had in mind for this time of year.
* '''Jack Frost:''' Don't most humans get heavier at Christmas?
* '''Player:''' Keep at it and I'll start to believe him instead of you.
* '''Jack Frost:''' Ok, ok!
* '''Jack Frost:''' Anyway, Anti-santa, behold! Time for [player name] to come crashing and crushing!
* {{tact|end}}

===Speaking to Jack Frost after the 10th snowball===
* '''Jack Frost:''' (whisper)I've made you denser. Slide into him and send him flying!
* {{tact|initial}}

===Sliding into Anti-Santa===
* {{tact|Anti-Santa gets sent flying backwards and lands on the ice}}
* {{qact|A cutscene starts. [[Winter Funfair]] begins to play.}}
* '''Anti-Santa:''' Ha Ha Ha I think I cracked a rib. I am impressed. This will do really nicely.
* '''Anti-Santa:''' Ha Ha Ha I will now go and wipe mirth off someone else's holidays.
* {{qact|Anti-Santa disappears into his portal}}
* '''Jack Frost:''' I hope I don't see you again!
* {{qact|Cutscene ends.}}
* '''Jack Frost:''' Let me make you less dense again.
* '''Player:''' Thank you. It really felt like I was made out of stone, out there.{{sic}}
* '''Jack Frost:''' I should have gone in front of you brushing the ice to make you go faster. Anyhow, you're back to being a stick.
* '''Player:''' Sticks and stones... Are you implying I would have cracked his rib either way?
* '''Jack Frost:''' Ice is pretty deadly, which is convenient because I don't think we would have talked him into leaving.
* '''Jack Frost:''' Now he's finally gone, I would like you to do me one last small favour.
* '''Player:''' Oh no.
* '''Jack Frost:''' It's not too bad, I promise. There's a wild goose over there. If you would kindly pet it for me?
* '''Player:''' A wild goose? With a hat? Wait. Are you literally sending me on a wild goose chase?
* '''Jack Frost:''' You caught me! But seriously, it's very soft and well worth a pet. Come back to me once you're done.
* {{tact|initial}}

===Talking to Jack Frost before finishing the cutscene===
* {{qact|Cutscene starts.}}
* {{tact|above}}

===Talking to Jack Frost after finishing the cutscene===
* '''Jack Frost:''' Let me make you less dense again.
* {{tact|above}}

==After Anti-Santa's defeat==
===Talking to Jack Frost again===
* '''Jack Frost:''' I just need you to pet that goose over there!
* {{tact|end}}

===Petting the Goose===
* '''Goose:''' {{overhead|*HONK*}}
* {{trandom}}
* {{topt|Dialogue 1}}
** '''Player:''' Of course, you honk. I don't know what I was expecting.
** {{tact|end}}
* {{topt|Dialogue 2}}
** '''Player:''' That is one large, loud chicken.
** {{tact|end}}
* {{topt|Dialogue 3}}
** '''Player:''' You're actually pretty cute with that little hat.
** {{tact|end}}
* {{topt|Dialogue 4}}
** '''Player:''' I take it that stealth is not your speciality.
** {{tact|end}}
* {{topt|Dialogue 5}}
** {{tbox|Looking closer at the goose's hat, it's got the name 'Wolfy' written on it.}}
** '''Player:''' I wonder where you came from?
** {{tact|end}}

===Talking to Jack Frost after petting the Goose===
* '''Jack Frost:''' Looks like you've still got both of your hands. That's lucky!
* '''Player:''' You are joking. Are you saying that goose could have had my hand off?
* '''Jack Frost:''' You caught me again! That goose has a fearsome name which it only reveals to a select few, but it's all HONK and no bite.
* '''Jack Frost:''' Anyhow, I don't think I can impose on your time anymore. I've had lots of fun thanks to you and I will have lots of stories to tell when I have dinner with dad after Christmas!
* '''Jack Frost:''' How I made you draw a heart, jump the shark, crush and defeat Anti-santa and how I topped it up by sending you on a wild goose chase from which you came back with both hands!
* '''Player:''' The most impressive thing here is that although they all sound like tall tales, they are all technically true! Feel free to send your dad to me if he doesn't believe you!
* '''Jack Frost:''' I can't thank you for your help without a little something. Here are a couple of cool things that I think would fit you well.
* {{tcond|If the player has insufficient inventory space:}}
** {{tbox|You need {{color|#ff0000|[number]}} free inventory slots to recieve your Christmas event rewards.}}
** {{tact|end}}
* '''Player:''' Yes, very 'cool' indeed. I see what you did there. Thank you!
* '''Jack Frost:''' Since you're still around, you know how I said I would give you a few challenges to keep you on your toes?
* '''Player:''' Mmm?
* '''Jack Frost:''' Well they are still there for you to complete. You get nothing for completing them except the knowledge that you have done something cool.
* '''Jack Frost:''' I've got a list here, which you can check any time.
* '''Jack Frost:''' As you seemed to have fun with the beacons earlier, I'm going to add beacons at random and you can keep collecting them if you like.
* '''Jack Frost:''' If you prefer, you can also have a go at challenge mode where I will add all the beacons at once and you have to collect them as fast as you can!
* {{tact|end}}

==Post event==
===Talking to Jack Frost===
* '''Jack Frost:''' Since you're still around, you know how I said I would give you a few challenges to keep you on your toes?
* {{tact|above}}

